{
    "poem_title": "- XXII - ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "author": "Argensola",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "Fili, en tus ojos mi atención respeta",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "(antes adora) aquellos altos fines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "que, ya su vaga luz tiendas o inclines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "muestran furor de indignación secreta.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Fili, en tus ojos mi atención respeta\n(antes adora) aquellos altos fines,\nque, ya su vaga luz tiendas o inclines,\nmuestran furor de indignación secreta."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "Así el tirano en pálido cometa,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "que horrendo vibra prodigiosas crines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "donde rayan sus lúcidos confines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "amenazas y estragos interpreta.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Así el tirano en pálido cometa,\nque horrendo vibra prodigiosas crines,\ndonde rayan sus lúcidos confines,\namenazas y estragos interpreta."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "Mas pues ya la piedad vence al destino,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "y el mismo horror en la severa lumbre",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "descubre al justo ostentación propicia,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mas pues ya la piedad vence al destino,\ny el mismo horror en la severa lumbre\ndescubre al justo ostentación propicia,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "anúncienos tu rostro mansedumbre;",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "que nunca por benigna la justicia",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "se contrapuso al disponer divino.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "anúncienos tu rostro mansedumbre;\nque nunca por benigna la justicia\nse contrapuso al disponer divino."
        }
    ]
}